tp.pr5.userInterfaces

Class MultipleGUIFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • tp.pr5.userInterfaces.InterfaceModesAbstractFactory
      • tp.pr5.userInterfaces.MultipleGUIFactory

  • public class MultipleGUIFactory
extends InterfaceModesAbstractFactory
    Factory for the multiple GUI interface mode.
    It has a field to select the number of synchronized GUI interfaces which you want to run.
    Author:
    Abel Serrano Juste
